<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Application Status Update - IECA</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 120px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .status-approved {
            background: #f0fdf4;
            border: 2px solid #22c55e;
            color: #15803d;
        }
        .status-rejected {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border: 2px solid #ef4444;
            color: #dc2626;
        }
        .status-box {
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #64748b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="cid:ieca-logo" alt="IECA Logo" class="logo">
            <h1>ðŸ“¬ Application Status Update</h1>
            <p>Indian Error Cyber Army - Membership Application</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
            
            <p>
                We have completed the review of your IECA membership application. Thank you for your patience during our evaluation process.
            </p>
            
            {{#if (eq status "approved")}}
            <div class="status-box status-approved">
                <h2>ðŸŽ‰ Congratulations! Application Approved</h2>
                <p>
                    Welcome to the Indian Error Cyber Army! Your application has been approved, and you are now an official member of India's premier cybersecurity community.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <p>
                <strong>What's Next:</strong>
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>You now have full access to all IECA resources and tools</li>
                <li>Join our exclusive global chat and connect with fellow cybersecurity professionals</li>
                <li>Participate in CTF challenges and training sessions</li>
                <li>Access our comprehensive cybersecurity library</li>
                <li>Receive regular threat intelligence updates</li>
            </ul>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{websiteUrl}}/portal/dashboard" class="cta-button">
                    Access Your Member Portal ðŸš€
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <p>
                We're excited to have you as part of our mission to strengthen India's cybersecurity infrastructure. Welcome aboard!
            </p>
            {{else}}
            <div class="status-box status-rejected">
                <h2>ðŸ“‹ Application Status: Not Approved</h2>
                <p>
                    After careful consideration, we are unable to approve your membership application at this time.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            {{#if reason}}
            <p>
                <strong>Feedback:</strong><br>
                {{reason}}
            </p>
            {{/if}}
            
            <p>
                <strong>Don't give up!</strong> We encourage you to:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Continue developing your cybersecurity skills and experience</li>
                <li>Engage with the cybersecurity community</li>
                <li>Consider applying again in the future (minimum 6 months)</li>
                <li>Reach out to us if you have specific questions about improving your profile</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>
                You can still access our public resources and stay connected with the cybersecurity community through our public channels.
            </p>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                <strong>Indian Error Cyber Army (IECA)</strong><br>
                Building India's Cybersecurity Future
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px;">
                For questions about your application, contact: applications@ieca.zehrasec.com
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
